assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Catenae Innovation Plc, together with its subsidiaries, provides financial technology and media publishing solutions primarily in the United Kingdom. The company offers COV-ID, a mobile application that contains a securely encrypted digital wallet, which provides demonstrable proof of an individual's Covid-19 status; OnSite WorkID, a digital wallet that allows the service provider to prove their identity and status to a third party; OnSite HospitalityID, an application that collects and stores customers details on each visit; OnSite TaskManager, a mobile management, inspection, and reporting solution; and OnSide, a centralized management tool for local government and community groups that offers scheduling of staff rotas, timesheet processing, attendee management, and reporting services. It also provides Sequestrum, a blockchain service that creates a permanent record of assets or transactions and provides the ability to act and report on activity relating to those assets or transactions. The company was formerly known as Milestone Group plc and changed its name to Catenae Innovation Plc in March 2018. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
